#

Truffle Parmesan Popcorn

15 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackQuickEasy

Description

A luxurious twist on classic popcorn, tossed in truffle oil and sprinkled with Parmesan for an irresistible snack!

Ingredients

  • popcorn kernels: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • truffle oil: 1 tablespoon
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup grated
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
